N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 150.7 - Compliance with other regulations

State Regulations

Compliance with the regulations in this Part shall not
excuse failure to comply with any other applicable laws or regulations of New

York State or other states or other countries. Notes
